		"name": "AI Services - ALL 12 E2E via NestJS",
		"description": "Complete E2E testing of ALL 12 AI services through the NestJS backend.\n\nFlow: Postman → NestJS (:3000, JWT auth) → Django (:8000, AI) → Groq LLM\n\nNew AI endpoints at: /api/v1/ai/*\n\nSetup:\n1. Start Django: cd AI_Study && python manage.py runserver 8000\n2. Start NestJS: cd apexiq-backend/apexiq && npm run start:dev\n3. Run '1. Auth' folder first to get JWT token\n4. Run '2. All 12 AI Services' to test everything\n\nAll tokens auto-save via test scripts — just run in order.",
